      <li parentName="ul">{`2.1.13 - Ensure that the `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`RotateKubeletServerCertificate`}</inlineCode>{` argument is set to true (Scored)`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`2.1.14 - Ensure that the Kubelet only makes use of Strong Cryptographic Ciphers (Not Scored)`}</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Audit`}</strong></p>
    <p>{`Inspect the Kubelet containers on all hosts and verify that they are running with the following options:`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul"><inlineCode parentName="li">{`--streaming-connection-idle-timeout=<duration greater than 0>`}</inlineCode></li>
      <li parentName="ul"><inlineCode parentName="li">{`--authorization-mode=Webhook`}</inlineCode></li>
