      <li parentName="ul">{`1.7.4 - Do not admit containers wishing to share the host network namespace (Not Scored)`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`1.7.5 - Do not admit containers with `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`allowPrivilegeEscalation`}</inlineCode>{` (Not Scored)`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`1.7.6 - Do not admit root containers (Not Scored)`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`1.7.7 - Do not admit containers with dangerous capabilities (Not Scored)`}</li>
